title: Raritan PX Devices Sensors: Contact
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/raritan
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors contact sensors connected to a Raritan PX device.
 Contact sensors can be on/off, contact, vibration, trip, water and smoke detection sensors
 No configuration is needed, the devices send their states by themselves.

item:
 The fixed statement {{Sensor}} followed by the sensor ID and the name of the sensor

discovery:
 One service is created for each sensor.
